README

collada_urdf_jsk_patch

collada_urdf_jsk_patch is a patched version of collada_urdf to use with assimp 3.1. hydro and ubuntu 12.04 provides assimp 2.0 and it has critical bag.

collada_urdf originally uses assimp but collada_urdf_jsk_patch uses assimp_devel. assimp_devel provides assimp 3.1.1.
